							href="https://themeforest.net/user/ashishmaraviya" target="_blank">Admin
							Dashboard</a>. All Rights Reserved.
					</p>
				</div>
			</footer>

		</div> <!-- End Page Wrapper -->
	</div> <!-- End Wrapper -->
    </div>
